e is a business\nrevival. The bulls therefore argue that, with money\nplentiful and confidence high, United States Steel will\nlead another advance in the stock market as it did last\nyear, and the year before and the one before that.\nThe trade revival is slow but sure. Julius Barnes made\none of the best surveys of the year and his conclusions\nwere sane and logical. Bankers agree with him, that ttfe\nyear 1930 as a whole is quite likely to balance 1929, and,\nwhat is more to the point, to go out with flying colors\nin contrast to last year\u2019s collapse.\nThe oil stocks appear to have taken the leaders of the\nindustry at their word.\nPacific Coast Utilities\nThe trio of west coast utilities,\nnamely, Pacific Gas, Pacific Light\ning and Southern California Edi\nson, have taken the limelight in\nthe utility group, and their for\nward progress in* recent sessions\nto new high levels for the year\nhave amply borne out the possi\nbilities for these stocks suggested\nin this column more than a\nmonth ago. All of these com\npanies have made promising in\nroads into the natural gas indus\ntry. in addition to the impressive\nprogress in earning power which\neach has demonstrated over the\npast number of years. In addi\ntion to these factors, constructive\nleaders have yet to stress the mer\nger possibilities so actively\nbrought forward in the, summer\nof fhst year.\nUnion Carbide\nDespite the generous ratio of\nearnings to current market valua\ntion that this stock is selling for.\nit is being pressed to the fore of\nthe general market list at every\nopportunity. Earnings for 1929\nwere in Um hiatort\n7*9 My\nSpinach\u2014Supplies, light; demand light;\nmarket, firm. Texas, bushel' baskets,\nSavoy type, *1.2591.36, meetly, *1.26.\nSlrawb*rriea \u2014Supplies, light, demand,\nlight; market firm. Florida, pony\nrefrigerators, various varieties, most\nmlssionarys, 87 \u00a94oc. mostly 460 per\nquart.\nOranges\u2014Supplies. light; demand,\nmoderaie, market, firns Florida